				<div class="hvres-header">			<div class="hvres-definition no-word">			<p class="hvres-spell"><a href="/hv/tiên">tiên</a><span class="hvres-operations"> <img src="/images/icon-permalink.png" title="Copy liên kết" onclick="CopyURLToClipboard(location.origin+'/whv/煎#pl7c0521727b')" /></span>			</p>			<p class="hvres-info gray small">phồn & giản thể</p>			</div>
